name: Rohu Fish
description: Rohu fish with head & tail pieces is rich in protein and low in fat. It also contains plenty of minerals such as zinc, iron, and calcium, and has an abundance of omega-3 fatty acids. Vitamins such as A and D are also present. This fish helps increase the "absorption rate", boosts immunity and has anti-inflammatory properties. It also enhances the skin, nails, and hair, regulates blood sugar, and prevents cardiovascular disease.

name: Salmon
description: Sink your teeth into the succulent, buttery flesh of Big Sam's Norwegian Salmon Fillet and be transported to the serene landscapes of Norway. Our expert fishermen navigate the frigid waters, harvesting only the best salmon to grace your plate. With two generous, skinless portions per pack, this offering is perfect for sharing or savoring for yourself.
